  "geo_edexcel_alevel_p2-2022-7-0": { summary: "Q3(c)/Q4(c) — Evaluate success of [regeneration strategy for Regenerating Places / OR integration for Diverse Places] [20m]", topic: "Shaping Places — evaluate strategy 20m 2022", markScheme: "20m (+4 SPaG): L4 (13-20m + SPaG): sustained analytical essay with specific evidence for both sides; clear evaluative conclusion. L3 (8-12m): analytical but less balanced. L2 (4-7m): some analysis. L1 (1-3m): mainly descriptive." },
