  "migration-2018-3-0": { summary: "Q04 — '[Statement about migration to Britain, e.g. Government policies were the main factor shaping migration to Britain.]' How far do you agree? [16m + 4 SPaG]", topic: "Migration 2018 — how far agree? [16+4 SPaG]", markScheme: "L4 (13-16m): Sustained, balanced argument explaining at least two aspects; well-supported overall judgement. AO1 (knowledge) up to 4m | AO2 (analysis) up to 12m. L3 (9-12m): Explains at least two aspects. L2 (5-8m): Some explanation of one or more aspects. L1 (1-4m): Simple, generalised comments." },

