  "nazigermany-2025-0-0": { summary: "Q01 — With reference to three sources, assess their value to a historian studying the appeal of the Nazi Party in Germany in the years 1929–33 [30m]", topic: "Appeal of Nazi Party 1929–33 — source value assessment [30m]", markScheme: "L5 (25-30m): Sustained evaluation of ALL THREE sources using NOP + contextual knowledge. Each source evaluated for value AND limitation. Cross-references sources. Clear overall judgement on relative value." },
  "nazigermany-2025-1-0": { summary: "Q02 — ‘Germany’s defeat in the First World War was the most important reason for the instability of the Weimar Republic in the years 1919–1923.’ Assess the validity of this view. [25m]", topic: "Weimar instability 1919–23 — WWI defeat most important? [25m]", markScheme: "L5 (21-25m): Well-organised analytical essay, balanced argument, well-substantiated judgement. Specific precise evidence. Full analytical treatment, conceptual awareness, clear conclusion. Must directly assess the stated view." },
