  "ocrcrimepunishment-2019-1-0": { summary: "Q1(b) — Give one reason why smuggling became widespread in Britain in the 18th century [1m]", topic: "Give one reason why smuggling became widespread in Britain in the", markScheme: "1m recall: give one specific, relevant example/reason/feature from the specified period." },
  "ocrcrimepunishment-2019-2-0": { summary: "Q1(c) — Give one way that the role of the police changed in Britain during the 20th century [1m]", topic: "Give one way that the role of the police changed in Britain durin", markScheme: "1m recall: give one specific, relevant example/reason/feature from the specified period." },
  "ocrcrimepunishment-2019-3-0": { summary: "Q2 — Write a clear and organised summary that analyses how crime changed in Britain between 1700 and 1900. Support your summary with examples. [9m]", topic: "Write a clear and organised summary that analyses how crime chang", markScheme: "L4 (8-9m): Clear, organised analytical summary explaining how/why the development evolved, using well-chosen examples integrated into analysis. L3 (5-7m): Organised with examples but less analytical. L2 (3-4m): Partly organised. L1 (1-2m): Isolated points." },
